        <title>Create a Blog With Hugo and Github</title>
        <link>http://isibox.github.io/post/create-blog-with-hugo-and-github/</link>
        <pubDate>Sat, 26 Feb 2022 16:28:56 +0100</pubDate>
        
        <guid>http://isibox.github.io/post/create-blog-with-hugo-and-github/</guid>
        <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;prerequisites-on-github&#34;&gt;Prerequisites on Github&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create a public respository &lt;strong&gt;blog_code&lt;/strong&gt; for storing the code.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create an another public repository &lt;strong&gt;mygithubname.github.io&lt;/strong&gt; to deploy (publish) the site. This one must have the same name as the Github username.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;open-a-shell-on-your-dev-environment&#34;&gt;Open a shell on your dev environment&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clone the blog_code respository.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;git clone git@github.com:isibox/blog_code.git
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Go to the blog_code folder.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#24909d&#34;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; blog_code
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;create-a-new-site-with-hugo&#34;&gt;Create a new site with Hugo&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;hugo new site cloud-guru-blog
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;install-a-theme-for-hugo&#34;&gt;Install a theme for Hugo&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Go to new site folder, and then in the themes folder.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#24909d&#34;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; ./cloud-guru-blog/themes
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Clone the themes you want to use.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;git clone https://github.com/CaiJimmy/hugo-theme-stack.git
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Go back to the site folder and rename the config.toml file site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#24909d&#34;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; ..
mv config.toml config.yml
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Configure the site to use the chosen theme&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-yaml&#34; data-lang=&#34;yaml&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;baseURL&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;http://isibox.github.io/&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;languageCode&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;en-us&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;title&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Cloud-Guru&amp;#39;s Blog&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;theme&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;hugo-theme-stack&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;create-a-first-post&#34;&gt;Create a first post&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;hugo new posts/my-first-post.md
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;And then, edit the file and write an simple example like below:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-yaml&#34; data-lang=&#34;yaml&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#447fcf;text-decoration:underline&#34;&gt;---&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;title&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;My First Post&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;date&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;2022-02-26T15:18:53&lt;span style=&#34;color:#3677a9&#34;&gt;+01&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#3677a9&#34;&gt;00&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;tags&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;- shortcodes&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;- code blocks&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;- mermaid&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#447fcf;text-decoration:underline&#34;&gt;---&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6ab825;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;A simple example of bash block code&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;```bash&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;echo &amp;#34;My first post with hugo&amp;#34;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;```&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Go back to your local source code repository and clone the push repository&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;git clone git@github.com:isibox/isibox.github.io.git

&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Go in deploy repository and create a new branch main. and then create an empty README.md file.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#24909d&#34;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; isibox.github.io
git checkout -b main
touch README.md
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Then commit the change:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;git status
git add .
git commit -m &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ed9d13&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;init commit&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;And then push the result:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;git push origin main
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now you should&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
